{
  "stem": "17337.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 277.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the beginning, I was working in the inside in the-- in the factory, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] doing all kinds of things with machines.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and then, then they sent me to work outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was the one who was building a-- for Schindler the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] stable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it took quite some time, you know, [LAUGHS] to finish that stable, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember one time-- we didn't have too much to eat by Schindler either because he couldn't-- he couldn't do nothing about food either, you know.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I remember one time-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were tracks not far from us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they brought, I don't know, two or three wagons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't know what's, what's in that-- wagons?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took some times to open the wagons because they were so frozen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were people inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Half of them were frozen to death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and they were Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Schindler took him-- took them to his factory, the inside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He gave them heated barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't have to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He gave them more food than he got.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he brought them back to, to, to, to life, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He brought them back to, to, to be a human.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the problem was that a lot of them were-- still were dying, a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because, you see, Hungarian Jews, they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the hunger was killing them more than a Polish Jew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You see, the Polish Jews were more hardened, hardened, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
